", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "body_html": "<p><code>Tensor.sum()</code> behaves as expected; <code>Variable.sum()</code> raises an overflow error:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-python\"><pre>torch.Tensor([<span class=\"pl-c1\">float</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>inf<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>)]).sum()\n<span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">#</span> inf</span>\n\ntorch.autograd.Variable(torch.Tensor([<span class=\"pl-c1\">float</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>inf<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>)])).sum()\n<span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">#</span> RuntimeError: value cannot be converted to type double without overflow: inf</span>\n\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">print</span>(torch.<span class=\"pl-c1\">__version__</span>)\n<span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">#</span> 0.2.0+c10898f</span></pre></div>", "body_text": "Tensor.sum() behaves as expected; Variable.sum() raises an overflow error:\ntorch.Tensor([float('inf')]).sum()\n# inf\n\ntorch.autograd.Variable(torch.Tensor([float('inf')])).sum()\n# RuntimeError: value cannot be converted to type double without overflow: inf\n\nprint(torch.__version__)\n# 0.2.0+c10898f", "body": "`Tensor.sum()` behaves as expected; `Variable.sum()` raises an overflow error:\r\n```py\r\ntorch.Tensor([float('inf')]).sum()\r\n# inf\r\n\r\ntorch.autograd.Variable(torch.Tensor([float('inf')])).sum()\r\n# RuntimeError: value cannot be converted to type double without overflow: inf\r\n\r\nprint(torch.__version__)\r\n# 0.2.0+c10898f\r\n```"}